property.name: note
property.value:
Stage 1, 2, and 3 switches are universal, at which point we need to move to either Acquittal or (Johanna's) Downfall. (Throw the appropriate switches for the choices the player makes. In the the Downfall timeline, there's one more stage switch, Stage 4, and BOTH timelines will use "END" to finish the party off when the time is right.
Oh, and set "LOSE" to lose the trial at any point.
